of Andalusia</a> deployment will be based on <a href="http://www.guadalinexedu.org">Guadalinex Edu</a>.</p>

<p>The Andalusian Information Society strategy is complemented with the
<a href="http://www.guadalinex.org">Guadalinex project</a>, aimed to citizen users.</p>
